ords":["ASL","American Sign Language","learn sign language"],"channelId":"UCZy9xs6Tn9vWqN_5l0EEIZA","isOwnerViewing":false,"shortDescription":"American Sign Language - ASL  \nLearn sign language at https://www.Lifeprint.com\nDonations appreciated (to help pay for hosting and related expenses). Please help:   \nhttps://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr?cmd=_s-xclick\u0026hosted_button_id=64QMBRBXQSV6G\nThanks!\nOr, if you prefer \"Cash App\" you can use: https://cash.me/$Lifeprint\nWant to order a USB drive with four semesters worth of ASL instruction? (ASL 1, ASL 2, ASL 3, and ASL 4)  for $79.95?  \nSee \"SuperUSB\" in the ASLUniversity bookstore at: https://lifeprint.com/bookstore/bookstore.htm\n\nFor free ASL Lessons see: https://www.youtube.com/billvicars\nTo learn basic fingerspelling see https://youtu.be/va1aAXpVr2w\n\nAbout your instructor:\nhttp://www.lifeprint.com/asl101/pages-layout/instructor.htm\nWarm regards and love to you all.\nI am grateful for your support.\n- Dr. Bill\n:)","isCrawlable":true,"thumbnail":{"thumbnails":[{"url":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/hMTxTnXCzOo/hqdefault.jpg?sqp=-oaymwEbCKgBEF5IVfKriqkDDggBFQAAiEIYAXABwAEG\u0026rs=AOn4CLC_aNutnM7yxAI7qL0Be-w3jXQT0Q","width":168,"height":94},{"url":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/hMTxTnXCzOo/hqdefault.jpg?sqp=-oaymwEbCMQBEG5IVfKriqkDDggBFQAAiEIYAXABwAEG\u0026rs=AOn4CLCqNJrP4fIYmUa05-y_iAy315dHLQ","width":196,"height":110},{"url":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/hMTxTnXCzOo/hqdefault.jpg?sqp=-oaymwEcCPYBEIoBSFXyq4qpAw4IARUAAIhCGAFwAcABBg==\u0026rs=AOn4CLA6wIp2scbkvzIfYPtyh7jNy6EUsg","width":246,"height":138},{"url":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/hMTxTnXCzOo/hqdefault.jpg?sqp=-oaymwEcCNACELwBSFXyq4qpAw4IARUAAIhCGAFwAcABBg==\u0026rs=AOn4CLAMbWebt4Q34hU84_QDzAz5dDssXQ","width":336,"height":188},{"url":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi_webp/hMTxTnXCzOo/maxresdefault.webp","width":1920,"height":1080}]},"allowRatings":true,"viewCount":"6587","author":"Signs","isPrivate":false,"isUnpluggedCorpus":false,"isLiveContent":false,"isTvfilmVideo":false}